Description:
Only Two Units on the Block, No Owner's Corporation. To Book your Private Inspection now, Call David Phua on 0401 803 110.
Just a short 5-minute walk from Dandenong Plaza is this cozy 2-bedroom unit that sits on a comfortable 220sqm of land, promising a simplistic & convenient lifestyle for downsizers, first-home buyers, and young families alike. With sizable indoor & outdoor spaces to enjoy, amongst various surrounding amenities, there's something for everyone here at this well-maintained home.
This brick-built home presents:
- 2 bedrooms with built-in-robes & plentiful natural light via bright windows
- Spacious living zone that connects seamlessly to the dining & kitchen area
- Kitchen boasting an abundance of storage, and quality appliances including a electric stovetop
- Bright bathroom with a neutral palette & feature tiling
- Separate laundry room with access to backyard
- Rear courtyard & expansive backyard
- Venetian & roller blinds throughout
- Split-system air conditioning
- 1-Car Garage
- Only Two Units on the Block, No Owner's Corporation
Clow Street Reserve is literally next door, and with a golf club, various sporting fields, and Dandenong Creek nearby, you're ensured a wholesome & natural lifestyle. The bus stop is only moments away, providing easy access to Dandenong Plaza where you'll find major retailers, Dandenong Market, cinemas, libraries, and more. Families will also appreciate the abundance of schools in your neighborhood, making this home one that surely ticks all the boxes for families of all shapes & sizes.
Chattels: All fittings and fixtures as inspected.
Deposit: 10%
Settlement Terms: 30 days.

Description:
THE ONE YOU ALL BEEN WAITING FOR..!
DANDENONG:
Area Specialist proudly presents to you 5 Lockington Crescent, this is a home built to bring out the finest family living experience. Characterized by meticulous attention to detail and premium craftsmanship, the entire floor plan of this 4 years young double storey Porter Davis benefits from abundant natural light and impressive indoor-outdoor living areas.
This masterpiece provides a stunning series of spaces across two stories of luxury living. A wonderfully impressive kitchen, pantry, open plan dining and not just one, but two living areas that beautifully underline the homes clever use of space dominate the ground floor. Adjacent to the kitchen is the verandah, which is equipped with separate kitchen designed to entertain family and friends all year round.
Upstairs there are four good size bedrooms, two master bedrooms with ensuite and WIR the other two bedrooms got built-in robes you also got the third living area or massive rumpus room for entertainment.
Located within a short distance of Dandenong Station, Dandenong Markets, Dandenong Plaza and picturesque parkland, this is an excellent spot for first-class family convenience. Youre also just moments from Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong High School.

Ray White is proud to present luxury living in the heart of Dandenong. This near new family residence is bound to charm even the fussiest of First Home Buyers, Upsizes and Investors. Quality built, situated in a highly desirable pocket of Dandenong, this home provides the ideal lifestyle you have been searching for!
This contemporary haven offers a spacious open plan lounge, kitchen and dining area on the ground floor. The lovely kitchen features stone benchtops, gas cooking, stainless steel appliances and ample cupboard space. The private low maintenance courtyard is perfect for outdoor enjoyment, the powder and laundry make up the rest of the ground floor.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with BIR and and full ensuite. Also upstairs are 2 good sized bedrooms with BIRs and luxurious bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles.
Features of this home include: single remote garage, split systems, ducted heating, garden shed and much more!
Located within a stone's throw away from Dandenong South Primary School, Dandenong Station, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!

Description:
Land, Location and Loads of Potential.
Situated on approximately 485m2, this is a developers dream on a RGZ1 site. You have the land - a spacious clean allotment with a north facing rear. You have the location - literally moments from central Dandenong, the Plaza, the station, and all its amenities. You have the potential and the possibility of building multiple dwellings (STCA). This weatherboard home is ripe for the picking. Buy it, build on it (STCA) and enjoy the bountiful rewards!
Look up and down the neighbouring streets and witness a number of multi-unit and dwelling sites that have been developed. This is another hub of Melbourne that is always growing, so why not buy and build! The location is second to none with its easy access to shos, cafes, bus stops, the train, plenty of primary and secondary schools plus more. The home itself currently has three bedrooms, a bathroom, living, kitchen with dining plus laundry.
Immerse yourself in a great opportunity in a rapidly transforming location with this 485m2 approx. allotment of pure Dandenong potential. When land is king, this is the site you will see value for development and a prosperous future. Don't miss out!

Description:
PLANS & PERMITS FOR 3 TOWNHOUSES ON 578SQM OF LAND APPROX
An excellent opportunity for builders, developers and investors, this prime property presents plans and permits for 3 sensational townhouses to be built on 578sqm of land (approx).. Walking distance to local sporting amenities, parks and Dandenong CBD gives future residents a fantastic range of amenities at their door step including Dandenong Market and Plaza, restaurants, cafes, cinema, schools, buses and trains as well as within easy access to Princes Highway, the Monash Freeway and Eastlink.
The established home comprises of large entrance with room for a study nook, an open plan kitchen, meals and living room with high ceilings, fireplace, split system air conditioner and original floorboards as well as two bedrooms, a central bathroom, separate WC and laundry.
Easy care grassed yards mean outside maintenance is a breeze and theres plenty of time to relax and unwind under the pergola. Two handy sheds provide valuable additional storage and a single garage plus driveway parking space cater for off street parking.
Open plan kitchen, meals and living, entrance with room for study nook, two bedroom, bathroom, WC and laundry
Low maintenance yards with grassed areas, two storage sheds, pergola and single garage
Original timber floorboards, high ceilings, fireplace and split system air conditioner
Superb location near shops, market, restaurants, cafes, cinema, schools, buses, trains, Princes Highway, the Monash Freeway and Eastlink
